CustomField.inlineHelpText:
JSON object example, keys are required:
{ "Fields": [
    {
     "api": "Field To Require API Value",
     "controllingField": "Controlling Field API Value",
     "controllingValues": [ "List of controlling values" ]
    },
    {
    Repeat the above for more values ie:
    "api": "RequredAPI",
    "controllingField": "RequiredController",
    "controllingValues": ["Value1", "Value2", "etc..."]
    } ]
}
